    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E36 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S50 inline-six engine with verified VANOS functionality. Power is delivered through a precise ZF 5-speed manual transmission and a factory 3.15 limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional power delivery and mid-corner stability. The chassis has been enhanced with a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed suspension geometry featuring Bilstein dampers and poly-bushed control arms. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul with a high-flow aluminum radiator. While the exterior displays a light, honest patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the analog feedback and telepathic steering response that defines this homologation-inspired platform.",
      "price": 34500.0,
