    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2017 Porsche Macan S in Volcano Grey Metallic, a vehicle that perfectly captures the balance between a sports car soul and SUV practicality. This Macan has been meticulously maintained and is in excellent mechanical health. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous finish, though minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch near the rear wheel arch are present upon close inspection\u2014typical of a well-cared-for daily driver. Inside, the black leather interior is clean and inviting; the seats remain firm and supportive, with only light creasing on the driver-side bolster. All electronic features, including the PCM navigation system, heated seats, and panoramic sunroof, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the 3.0L twin-turbo V6 runs smoothly, benefited by a documented service history at Porsche-certified technicians. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service, new cabin air filters, and a brake pad replacement within the last 5,000 miles. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, and the car drives straight and true with no vibrations or unusual noises. This is a turn-key luxury crossover ready for its next owner. Includes two keys, original manuals, and a complete set of all-weather floor mats.",
